I'll tell you the same.

30:43.710 --> 30:46.311
[ Chuckles ]

30:46.313 --> 30:48.213
Um...

30:50.250 --> 30:51.583
I'm Jay Singletary.

30:51.585 --> 30:54.186
I, uh...

30:54.188 --> 30:56.455
Oh, I saw the tail end
