41:42.303 --> 41:45.370
Murdered.

41:45.372 --> 41:46.772
What's going on?

41:46.774 --> 41:50.041
It was that boy Nero
who was calling you.

41:50.043 --> 41:51.777
You remember that boy
that kept calling?

41:51.779 --> 41:53.112
I never thought
he would.

41:53.114 --> 41:54.113
No, no.

41:54.115 --> 41:57.048
He got his tongue...

41:57.050 --> 42:01.320
cut out and tied into a knot.

42:01.322 --> 42:03.455
You ever heard of something
like that?

42:03.457 --> 42:05.791
Terrence: It just don't make
no sense, Mama.

42:05.793 --> 42:07.659
♪♪

42:07.661 --> 42:10.595
I just
can't understand it.

42:10.597 --> 42:13.532
This ain't
Mississippi.

42:13.534 --> 42:16.467
-[ Indistinct ]
-I'm so sorry.

42:16.469 --> 42:20.271
I know you known that boy
a long time.

42:20.273 --> 42:24.243
[ Door opens ]

42:28.949 --> 42:31.016
[ Dog barking in distance ]

42:31.018 --> 42:34.253
[ Indistinct shouting
in distance ]

42:46.567 --> 42:49.501
What the hell?!

42:49.503 --> 42:51.102
Girl, you scared me.

42:51.104 --> 42:53.505
There's something going on,
Terrence.

42:55.843 --> 42:57.943
I can't stay here.

43:00.581 --> 43:03.849
It's not safe.

43:03.851 --> 43:06.317
Please, you can --
you can drop me at a hotel or...

43:06.319 --> 43:08.653
or somewhere.

43:08.655 --> 43:10.455
I just can't stay here.

43:10.457 --> 43:13.725
Man, what happened
to Nero...

43:13.727 --> 43:15.660
it's weird, man.

43:15.662 --> 43:17.462
You know, shit happens.

43:17.464 --> 43:19.999
Nero messes
with the wrong cats.

43:20.001 --> 43:24.335
Easystreeters been running up
in here for weeks.

43:24.337 --> 43:25.971
But not like this.

43:29.410 --> 43:31.043
Please.

43:33.680 --> 43:36.548
♪♪

43:41.489 --> 43:44.423
