on the floor first.

44:25.332 --> 44:27.132
[ Scoffs ] Nah, come on.
T-There's...

44:27.134 --> 44:31.069
No, please.
Just let me be on the couch.

44:31.071 --> 44:34.139
It's perfect.

44:34.141 --> 44:37.675
Uh, well...

44:37.677 --> 44:39.945
Can I use your phone?

44:39.947 --> 44:41.413
I'll pay.

44:41.415 --> 44:43.681
Yeah.

44:43.683 --> 44:45.150
Thanks.

44:45.152 --> 44:47.052
♪♪

44:50.624 --> 44:54.460
