45:10.578 --> 45:12.378
What the hell
do you want?

45:12.380 --> 45:15.914
I just didn't want you
to be worried.

45:15.916 --> 45:17.649
So?

45:17.651 --> 45:20.652
I'm not staying
at Big Momma's anymore.

45:20.654 --> 45:22.921
Well,
where you staying at?

45:22.923 --> 45:27.125
With a friend.
[ Sighs ]

45:27.127 --> 45:29.795
You better get
your stupid ass home.

45:29.797 --> 45:32.398
You're gonna get yourself
in all kinds of trouble.

45:32.400 --> 45:35.934
I -- I can't do that,
Mama.

45:35.936 --> 45:38.270
There's something
going on.

45:38.272 --> 45:42.674
Well, if you don't come home,
I'm gonna come get you.

45:42.676 --> 45:43.809
What do you know
about it, Mama?

45:43.811 --> 45:46.078
You know something.

45:46.080 --> 45:48.614
What about all this?

45:48.616 --> 45:50.749
What about George Hodel?

45:50.751 --> 45:52.284
I'm coming to L.A.

45:52.286 --> 45:55.287
[ Dial tone ]

45:57.425 --> 45:58.957
♪♪

46:00.560 --> 46:01.860
Thank you.

46:03.763 --> 46:06.432
What are you doing here?

46:06.434 --> 46:08.900
I'd go home if I was you.

46:08.902 --> 46:11.036
I can't let it go.

46:11.038 --> 46:14.106
If you go looking for trouble,
